keywhiz.generators

Interface SecretGeneratorFactory<RequestType>

  • Type Parameters:
    RequestType - parameter of resultant generator.

    public interface SecretGeneratorFactory<RequestType>
    Factory to produce SecretGenerators. Implement this factory to produce generators. Keywhiz will call the create method and supply necessary dependencies as arguments.
